Kris Statlander dressed as Goku Black on the Halloween edition of AEW Dynamite

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/eb9710d6-bcff-40a5-9237-c3ee3626978d/processed_21886.jpg?format=original)

## **_"uhh.. blood and guts."_**

## **_\- Orange Cassidy_**

*   ## **_The Death Riders vs Darby Allin, Mark Briscoe, Kyle O'Reilly, Roderick Strong and Orange Cassidy in Blood and Guts is officially on!_**
    

Jon Moxley vs Kyle O'Reilly goes to a double countout. Post match Marina Shafir attacks Aubrey Edwards and the Death Riders jump Kyle.

Roderick Strong and the rest of the Conglomeration run out and clear the ring before Mark Briscoe forces Orange Cassidy to lazily make the challenge 😂

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/42ce5b22-4329-4dd7-b3a1-ab169af094d2/21890.jpg?format=original)

Bandido and Grandido ♥️

We get a big ol baby face video package of Bandido bringing his grandma to watch him wrestle for her first time as he faced Kazuchika Okada

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0a285d49-a3e6-45aa-a75d-27c55daeccc4/processed_21893.jpg?format=original)

Mercedes Moné and Athena jumped Kris Statlander until Willow Nightengale and Harley Cameron run out for the save.

Willow and Harley will take on Mercedes and Athena next week in the first round of the AEW Women's World Tag Team Championship Tournament

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d7c57497-79a5-463d-8063-94f089a625dd/21903.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AEW Women's Tag Team Championship Tournament: Sisters of Sin def. Jamie Hayter and Queen Aminata after Thekla interferes and takes out Hayter behind the referee's back_**
    

Backstage, Penelope Ford reveals she is out of action indefinitely and Megan Bayne will need a partner.

Bayne says she was dominating before she teamed with Ford so anyone can step up. Marina Shafir and Jon Moxley walk up.

A new team is formed.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/65bde7c7-89dd-41f8-8f4b-2cb26cc3756a/processed_21911.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AEW World Championship Number One Contender: Samoa Joe def Hook, Ricochet, and Bobby Lashley_**
    

Bobby Lashley almost made it back into the ring after Ricochet hit him with a chair and made him leave the ring, but Lashley was too late to break up the submission and Hook tapped out.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/daaaa58f-87c4-4e30-910b-dedfc7483dc3/21922.jpg?format=original)

Tony Shiavonne invites Samoa Joe to the ring for an impromptu contract signing with the help of some jobbers in Halloween costumes.

The Opps are too smart for this so they attack the costumed jobbers but they REALLY ARE just jobbers.

Tony Shiavonne calls for a toast. The Opps are toasting when Tony calls for a toast to Hangman Adam Page.

AND THEN TONY SHIAVONNE REVEALS HE WAS HANGMAN ADAM PAGE ALL ALONG

They were using his voice over the arena loudspeakers the entire time.

Hangman Shiavonne takes out the Opps to end Dynamite